game.name: Beauty And Unicorn
game.description:
The beautiful princess and her beloved horse have a plan to attend the palace banquet today. However, this gorgeous girl slipped at her home and all her dress got spoiled immediately. She is looking very tense now and seeking help from someone like you who are blessed with cool fashion designer skills. Would you try out this challenging task right away? If so, join Beauty And Unicorn gazme to dress her up perfectly before the departure of the two in this brand new dressing game. 

Barbie loves to attend a party, and her beloved magical unicorn is waiting outside for her. It will be completely on your hands how quickly you give her complete makeover to look fabulous on this special occasion. She relies on your unique fashion talents, so just browse through a wide range of dresses and other accessories to help her finalize an awesome outfit. Try to be a little bit fast to make her look gorgeous! Make sure to give her a valuable dress suggestion before taking off on her flying unicorn in this html5 dress up game.
